{"tid":2515733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓為稱中國為「戇鳩死毒撚」致歉 改稱「武漢肺炎大恩人」","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:13:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c6464326f5d53823120331a8f14e0d15d7e3685b","tid":2515733,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"菲國外長就發表帶粗口帖文道歉 總統稱中國是恩人<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓外長洛欽就他在社交網站發表帶有粗口的帖文，要求中國船隻離開兩國有主權爭議水域，向中方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n總統府發言人說，洛欽已經向中國大使致歉，又引述洛欽表示，發表有關言論是因為有些事惹怒了他。<br />\n<br />\n總統杜特爾特強調，中國仍然是菲律賓的恩人，雖然菲律賓與中國之間發生衝突，但並不意味菲方要變得無禮，不尊重別人，菲律賓事實上亦有太多事要感謝中國，無論是過去的幫助，或者是現在的協助。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特昨日接種中國國藥集團的新冠疫苗，他在接種後表示感覺不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=36636aba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=261bb5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6c3af2a028bcc905ce46fa3729ab966c4df148a5","tid":2515733,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"杜特爾特正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7dda40f97c40dc66a04c494b127d8da23898b9","tid":2515733,"uid":371175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"識玩 彈出彈入 撚完人之後道個歉 吹佢唔脹"},{"pid":"23a3eb54e35054c46181bb20f1c8b21cb0a71e1c","tid":2515733,"uid":393495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7dda40f97c40dc66a04c494b127d8da23898b9","tid":2515733,"uid":371175,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"識玩 彈出彈入 撚完人之後道個歉 吹佢唔脹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"未必係你咁諗，中國填海填到去菲律賓外面嘅專屬經濟區，總統係堅跪"},{"pid":"8abd02a885311848bd27d153edffb8cd16e240cb","tid":2515733,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"杜特爾特曾經都講過菲律賓可以成為中國一部份<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/szExsjZDCnM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FszExsjZDCnM&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=cf7405d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/szExsjZDCnM</a><br />\n但是,下面個班就睬佢都傻<br />\n馬尼拉市長重講明,馬尼拉從來都唔係中國一部份<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B0NunEHkkPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB0NunEHkkPY&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=27a1a507\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B0NunEHkkPY</a>"},{"pid":"08f4f360d7f8decf6617bbf8c4be0c869aa9f45d","tid":2515733,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca78b30104a6caeb66c95fb2cef54abf39b1ca67","tid":2515733,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"二次傷害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4af43944c0c6bc4ca61643eca74b07759c9682a","tid":2515733,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"sor9ry 咯"},{"pid":"4d632db83e4c14acf4d6b6554b45d0e1b8664fe2","tid":2515733,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"呢個廢老幾時可以處死？"},{"pid":"64febda11e33c9c27376b592aae8fbaf14d6955d","tid":2515733,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"支共呢排無過數咩？"},{"pid":"a2efe89f509e52b16c427ec1d756d5675abd7b81","tid":2515733,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\